<p>

<ul>
<li>
R. Harper and J. Mitchell.
<!WA6><A HREF="http://www.cs.cmu.edu:8001/afs/cs/user/rwh/public/papers/xml.ps">
On the type structure of Standard ML</A>.
<cite>Trans. Programming Languages and Systems</cite>, 15(2):211--252,
Apr. 1993.
</ul>

